quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  3,42,Bak saboh masa malaikat kheun Wahe Mariyam pilehan Allah Gata le Tuhan ka Neupeusuci Neupileh lagi raya that tuah Ngon bandum inong nyang na lam alam Gata Mariyam leubeh that ceudah
  3,43,Wahe Mariyam pubuet ibadat Tasujud ligat tapujoe Allah Ruku‘ ngon sujud ngon ureueng saleh Ureueng teuleubeh geunaseh Allah
  3,44,Nyan haba gaeb Kamoe bri wahyu Bak gata Nabi jinoe meupeugah Hana roh gata sajan awaknyan Watee awak nyan meutaroh tuah Meutiek-tiek kalam soe-soe nyang meunang Nyan nyang peutimang Maryam meutuah Hana roe gata sajan awaknyan Watee awak nyan meubantah-bantah
  3,45,Malaikat kheun wahe Mariyam Amanah Tuhan saboh kalimah Nyang akan lahe sinan bak gata Al-Masih Isa Tuhan Neupeugah Jeut keupemuka donya akhirat Deungon Hadharat pih toe that leupah
  3,46,Seujak lam ayon ka jeut geumarit € Yoh mantong ubit manyak sileupah Sampoe ‘oh tuha Tuhan peuleubeh Ureueng nyang saleh Neubri le Allah
  3,47,"Han tom teupeh lon ngon ureueng agam Pane jeut meunan aneuk tan ayah Geukheun ka meunan Neukheun le Tuhan Ban nyang h‘eut Tuhan Neupeujeut bagah Neukheun \"kun\" mantong ‘oh Neumeung peugo Sit jeut le siat hana meupayah"
  3,48,Neupeureunoe lom kitab ngon hikmat € Meunan pih Taurat kitab nyang sudah Ngon kitab Injil dum seukalian
  3,49,Lom rasul Tuhan gopnyan Neupeugah Rasul Tuhan bak Bani Israil Tanda bak Rabbi nyoe lon peuleumah Lon peugot ticem nibak tanoh kliet Lon buliet-buliet lon pruh lon rajah Ka jeut keu ticem jipe le ligat Nyan saboh ayat ngon izin Allah Jeut lon peupuleh lom ureueng buta Ngon seupot lanja puleh le bagah Jeut lon peuudep ureueng nyang mate Kon deungon sihe ngon izin Allah Lom pih lon peugah peue nyang tapajoh Lom peue nyang tatroh nyang jeut takeubah Nyang jeut takeubah di rumoh gata Bandum sigala abeh lon peugah Di sinan sit jeut keu saboh tanda Meunyo na gata iman keu Allah
  3,50,Taurat nyang dilee pih lon peubeuna Peuhaleu teuma ladom nyang salah Nyang dilee hareum ladom keu gata Jinoe haleu ka Neukheun le Allah Lon ba ngon ayat bak Tuhan gata Teuma takwa bandum keu Allah Tataʻat keu Lon teuma dum gata
  3,51,Allah Taʻala sidroe taseumah Allah Tuhanlon ngon Tuhan gata Laen sigala Tuhan nyang salah Nyoe keuh nyang lon ba jalan nyang teupat Nyang laen meuhat bandum takeubah
  3,52,‘Oh ban geurasa le Nabi Isa Awak nyan nyata kaphe keu Allah Geukheun bak rakan teuma wateenyan Soe tem bantu lon bak jalan Allah Teuma seuot le dum kawariyyun Kamoe nyang tulong agama Allah Kamoe meuiman gata keu saksi Kamoe seurah diri keupada Allah
  3,53,Hai Tuhan kamoe kamoe meuiman Peue nyang Neupeutron beuna sileupah Lom kamoe ikot peurintah Rasul Teuma Neukabui nyang kamoe peugah Neutuleh kamoe sajan ngon saksi Nyang gaseh Rabbi ureueng meutuah
  3,54,Teuma jitaki dum le awaknyan Teuma di Tuhan taki Neubalah Nyang leupah that got bak balah taki Tan laen lagi meulengkan Allah